---
title: Pan-Seared Chicken & Barley with Creamy Mushroom Sauce & Roasted Carrots
description: It’s like having Sunday supper any day of the week! Tender chicken cutlets are dusted in a savory spice blend, pan-fried and topped with a rich and creamy sauce that’s packed with earthy mushrooms. Served up with a side of pleasantly chewy barley and caramelized carrots. You won’t have to call ‘em twice to the dinner table for this one!
